      <title>印度尼西亚人离开正在喷发的火山附近的房屋，机场因火山灰危险而关闭</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/2024/04/18/1245497393/indonesians-leave-homes-near-erupting-volcano-and-airport-closes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于火山灰蔓延、岩石落下以及可能发生海啸的危险，印度尼西亚当局周四关闭了一座机场，居民离开了一座正在喷发的火山附近的房屋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/2024/04/18/1245497393/indonesians-leave-homes-near-erupting-volcano-and-airport-closes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 08:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
